The paper deals with the analysis of strings and their properties, which falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of binary words suggests a connection to formal languages (cs.FL) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The lower bound obtained using a family of binary words also suggests a connection to discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
